text: Epping on the London Underground is the north-eastern terminus of the Central Line. The station before Epping is Theydon Bois. Epping station is in the Epping Forest District of Essex. It is one of eight London Underground stations in this District and is in Travelcard Zone 6. ==References== Category:Central line stations Category:Transport in Epping Forest Category:London Travelcard zone 6 Category:1865 establishments in the United Kingdom
